=== EXAMPLE: scdoc_Guides_Tour_of_UGens_ex62 ===

DESCRIPTION: A very_bright noisy sound, with noise oscillator character around 52 Hz, featuring punchy attack and impulsive envelope, with chaotic spectral movement, filtered with steep_rolloff character, and spectrally dense.

CATEGORIES:
  attack_time: punchy
  brightness: very_bright
  crest_factor_db: impulsive
  envelope_flatness: very_dynamic
  harmonic_to_noise_ratio: noisy
  spectral_complexity_mean: dense
  spectral_flux_normalized: chaotic
  spectral_slope: steep_rolloff
  temporal_centroid: balanced

SYNTHESIS CONCEPTS (key values):
[oscillator]
  fundamental_freq: 51.6142
  harmonic_decay_rate: 0.0205
  harmonic_regularity: 0.0366
  pitch_clarity: 0.8441
  inharmonicity: 0.0420
  type: noise
[filter]
  spectral_slope: -0.0362
  resonance_freq: 0.0000

SUPERCOLLIDER CODE:
// Title: Tour of UGens Example 62
// Author: SC Documentation
// URL: http://doc.sccode.org/Guides/Tour_of_UGens.html
// Tags: Tour_of_UGens, Guides
// ---
// --- Example 62 ---
{ WhiteNoise.ar * Decay2.ar(Impulse.ar(1), 0.2, 0.9, 0.2) }.play;
{ WhiteNoise.ar * Decay2.ar(Dust.ar(3), 0.2, 0.9, 0.2) }.play;
